    "He revised a handbook originally written by the museum's <a href=\"/friedlanderm\">Max J. Friedl\u00e4nder</a>, in a much expanded form in 1924 as, <em>Die Altniederl\u00e4ndisch Malerei von 1400-1600</em>, as a volume in the prestigious Propyl\u00e4en Kunstgeschichte series.": [],
